quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  29,7,"Àwọn tó bá gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, dájúdájú A máa ha àwọn iṣẹ́ aburú wọn dànù fún wọn. Dájúdájú A ó sì san wọ́n lẹ́san pẹ̀lú èyí tó dára ju ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́.",""
  29,8,"A pa á ní àṣẹ fún ènìyàn láti ṣe dáadáa sí àwọn òbí rẹ̀ méjèèjì. Tí àwọn méjèèjì bá sì jà ọ́ lógun pé kí ó fi ohun tí ìwọ kò ní ìmọ̀ nípa rẹ̀ ṣẹbọ sí Mi, má ṣe tẹ̀lé àwọn méjèèjì.<sup>1</sup> Ọ̀dọ̀ Mi ni ibùpadàsí yín. Nítorí náà, Mo máa fún yín ní ìró ohun tí ẹ̀ ń ṣe níṣẹ́.","[1] Fífi ohun tí ẹ̀dá kò nímọ̀ nípa rẹ̀ ṣẹbọ sí Allāhu - Ọba tí kò ní akẹgbẹ́ - túmọ̀ sí pé, sísọ n̄ǹkan kan di ọlọ́hun, olúwa àti olùgbàlà lẹ́yìn Allāhu, n̄ǹkan tí Allāhu kò fi ìmọ̀ nípa n̄ǹkan náà mọ àwa ẹ̀dá Rẹ̀ nínú àwọn Tírà Rẹ̀ gẹ́gẹ́ bí “akẹgbẹ́ Rẹ̀”."
  29,9,"Àwọn tó bá gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe iṣẹ́ rere, dájúdájú A máa fi wọ́n sínú àwọn ẹni rere.",""
  29,10,"Ó ń bẹ nínú àwọn ènìyàn, ẹni tó ń wí pé: “A gba Allāhu gbọ́.” Nígbà tí wọ́n bá sì fi ìnira kàn án nínú ẹ̀sìn Allāhu, ó máa mú ìnira àwọn ènìyàn gẹ́gẹ́ bí ìyà ti Allāhu. (Ó sì máa padà sínú àìgbàgbọ́.) Tí àrànṣe kan láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ bá sì dé, dájúdájú wọn yóò wí pé: “Dájúdájú àwa wà pẹ̀lú yín.” Ṣé Allāhu kọ́ l’Ó nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ohun tí ń bẹ nínú igbá-àyà gbogbo ẹ̀dá ni?",""
  29,11,"Dájúdájú Allāhu máa ṣàfi hàn àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. Ó sì máa ṣàfi hàn àwọn ṣọ̀be-ṣèlu mùsùlùmí.",""
  29,12,"Àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ wí fún àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo pé: “Ẹ tẹ̀lé ojú ọ̀nà tiwa nítorí kí á lè ru àwọn ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ yín.” Wọn kò sì lè ru kiní kan nínú ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ wọn. Dájúdájú òpùrọ́ mà ni wọ́n.",""
  29,13,"Dájúdájú wọn yóò ru ẹrù ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ tiwọn àti àwọn ẹrù ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ kan mọ́ ẹrù ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ tiwọn. Àti pé dájúdájú A óò bi wọ́n léèrè ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde nípa ohun tí wọ́n ń dá ní àdápa irọ́.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah an-Nahl; 16:25"
  29,14,"Dájúdájú A rán (Ànábì) Nūh níṣẹ́ sí ìjọ rẹ̀. Ó gbé láààrin wọn fún ẹgbẹ̀rún ọdún àfi àádọ́ta ọdún. Ẹ̀kún-omi sì gbá wọn mú nígbà tí wọ́n jẹ́ alábòsí.",""
